race.description: Tumblong Hills Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: TREASURE HUNTER (6) handy gelding ready to win at his third race start. Stalked the speed when a gallant second over 1100m at Nowra.Will roll forward and take catching in this easier contest. SILVER SERENADE (12) has been kept fresh since she gripped on late for a tough third over 1100m at Goulburn. Ran third in a recent Goulburn trial over 800m. Shapes as a top-three player. DANCING MUMMA (11) covered ground from the outside draw on debut when a plugging third over 1100m at Nowra. Stable have a good record at this carnival. Keep safe. SPEED OF THOUGHT (9) improving mare who gets weight relief from the good gate after retuning with a solid fourth over 1000m at Queanbeyan. Will give plenty of cheek.
